OL,3,CGovernment to back huge loan to JLR in
OL,4,Corder to save supply chain
OL,6,FThe government is preparing to
OL,7,Funderwrite a substantial loan to
OL,8,FJaguar Land Rover so the company can
OL,9,Favoid insolvencies in its supply chain.
OL,11,FMinisters have been trying to work out
OL,12,Fhow to structure emergency taxpayer
OL,13,Fsupport ever since the company warned
OL,14,Ftwo weeks ago that the cyber attack it
OL,15,Fis battling is deeper and more complex
OL,16,Fthan the hacks that hit M&S and the Co-
OL,17,Fop, and that some of its suppliers are
OL,18,Funlikely to survive without help.
