OL,3,CGovernment to back huge loan to JLR in
OL,4,Corder to save supply chain
OL,6,FJLR has not made a car for 27 days and
OL,7,Fcounting. No new orders for parts have
OL,8,Fbeen placed, leaving more than 700
OL,9,Fbusinesses with reduced - and in some
OL,10,Fcases no - income to cover wages or
OL,11,Fbills.
OL,13,FThe supply chain is steadily running
OL,14,Fout of cash.
OL,16,FTo keep it afloat, ITV News
OL,17,Funderstands JLR is working with the
OL,18,FTreasury and the Department for
OL,19,FBusiness and Trade on an emergency
OL,20,Ffinancing scheme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
