OL,3,CGovernment to back huge loan to JLR in
OL,4,Corder to save supply chain
OL,6,FThe JLR plans to use the taxpayer-
OL,7,Fbacked loan to allow suppliers to draw
OL,8,Fdown cash early, using invoices or
OL,9,Fconfirmed orders as collateral. That
OL,10,Fmeans they can be paid for work before
OL,11,Fthe normal payment terms kick in. For
OL,12,Fsuppliers struggling to make payroll,
OL,13,Fit could be the difference between
OL,14,Fsurvival and closure.
OL,16,FThe idea is not risk-free.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
