OL,3,CGovernment to back huge loan to JLR in
OL,4,Corder to save supply chain
OL,6,FIf production takes longer than
OL,7,Fexpected to resume - and there is
OL,8,Fstill no timeline for a restart - some
OL,9,Ffirms may not be able to repay those
OL,10,Floans.
OL,12,FJLR has agreed to step in where a
OL,13,Fsupplier depends entirely on its
OL,14,Fbusiness, but warned it cannot take
OL,15,Fresponsibility for companies that also
OL,16,Fsupply other carmakers.
