OL,3,CGovernment to back huge loan to JLR in
OL,4,Corder to save supply chain
OL,6,FMinisters are wary of sending a signal
OL,7,Fthat companies whose computer systems
OL,8,Fare hacked can rely on the taxpayer to
OL,9,Fbail them out. But they accept that
OL,10,Fthe cyber attack on JLR is a threat to
OL,11,Fthe wider British car industry.
OL,13,FThe government has agreed to provide a
OL,14,Ffinancial backstop because, without
OL,15,Fit, JLR's rescue plan would move too
OL,16,Fslowly, weighed down by the due
OL,17,Fdiligence demanded by banks and
OL,18,Fcreditors.
