OL,3,CGovernment to back huge loan to JLR in
OL,4,Corder to save supply chain
OL,6,FOne industry source told me the
OL,7,Fsituation at JLR is an "existential
OL,8,Fthreat" and that some suppliers are
OL,9,F"days, not weeks, away from failing" -
OL,10,Fa warning echoed by Liam Byrne MP in
OL,11,Fhis letter to the chancellor on Friday.
OL,13,FJLR and the government have been
OL,14,Ftrying, with the support of the SMMT,
OL,15,Fto "map" the company's supply chain
OL,16,Fand assess the scale of financial
OL,17,Fdistress. A task made more difficult
OL,18,Fbecause much of the company's computer
OL,19,Fsystems remain offline due to the hack.
