OL,3,CGovernment to back huge loan to JLR in
OL,4,Corder to save supply chain
OL,6,FAs ITV News revealed on Thursday, the
OL,7,FBusiness Secretary Peter Kyle had been
OL,8,Fexploring a "buyer of last resort"
OL,9,Fscheme - where the government would
OL,10,Fpurchase parts directly from suppliers
OL,11,Fto avoid job losses - but this plan
OL,12,Fnow appears to have been shelved.
OL,14,FIn an interview with ITV News on
OL,15,FMonday, the chancellor described
OL,16,FJaguar Land Rover as the "Best of
OL,17,FBritish" and "one of (the UK's) most
OL,18,Fsuccessful companies".
